text: Oulad Aissa, Tunisia is a place in Tunisia, North Africa that is located at 36°32'12.0"N 10°13'35.0"E. It is north of Zagouan, and 20 kilometer south of Tunis. The area is mountainous.Oulad Aissa, Tunisia at google maps. == References == Category:Populated places in Tunisia
